    dc:description "Figure 56. Hyalonema stet. CCZ _ 081 A in situ image, B. Scale bars: 1 cm (A); 5 mm (B). Image attribution: Durden and Smith (A); Wiklund, Durden, Drennan, and McQuaid (B)." ;
